@startuml MCP-System-Architecture-Simple

title MCP LLM Generator System Architecture

package "VS Code (MCP Client)" {
  [UI Display]
  [Server Management]
  [Tool Cache]
  [Lifecycle Control]
}

package "MCP Servers" {
  [llm-generator]
  [assoc-memory]
  [mcp-shell-server]
  [google]
}

package "Storage" {
  database "SQLite"
  database "ChromaDB"
  file "Logs"
  file "Cache"
}

[VS Code (MCP Client)] ||--|| [MCP Servers] : stdio/JSON-RPC
[llm-generator] --> SQLite
[assoc-memory] --> ChromaDB
[mcp-shell-server] --> Logs
[google] --> Cache

note right of [VS Code (MCP Client)]
  Lifecycle Management
  - Start/Stop servers
  - Auto-start on demand
  - Cache tool info
end note

@enduml
